Speaker 1: Hey Sexton, this is KT Goodrich with Pfizer score blue bud. I'm going to use your 938 number to pull up your account.

Speaker 2: I want to read off what's on your chart so I can help you put a stop to this.

Speaker 1: Just help me verify some things. All right, bud.

Speaker 2: Uh-huh.

Speaker 1: So when I read this I see that you were working with Dr. Thomas Botini and he's one of our Pfizer doctors.

Speaker 2: Looks like he set you up as a VIP and then he wrote a script for the Cialis.

Speaker 1: Um, the 20 milligram generic that's from our—

Speaker 2: Pfizer labs in France. It's the FDA approved ones. It's um—

Speaker 1: Then I do see something peculiar. Dr. Botini has ordered the pharmacy to send you refills on his behalf.

Speaker 2: Um, I'm going to put a stop to this. Just hold your line. All right, bud. That way you don't get them.

Speaker 1: All right, one moment.
